PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts, as of December 31, 1998, by transferring the remaining balances in the 1991-1992 pool accounts for WHEAT, AMBER DURUM WHEAT and BARLEY, and in the 1985-1986, 1987-1988, 1988-1989, 1989-1990, 1990-1991 and 1991-1992 pool accounts for DESIGNATED BARLEY, to a separate account, and (b) to make a FINAL PAYMENT to producers entitled to them.
